---
import LegalPage from "../components/LegalPage.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Refund Policy - Aizen"
  description="Refund guidance for Aizen Pro purchases."
  canonicalPath="/refund"
  ogType="article"
>
  <LegalPage title="Refund Policy" lastUpdated="April 10, 2026">
    <section>
      <h2>30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
      <p>
        We want you to be satisfied with Aizen Pro. If you are not happy with your purchase for any
        reason, you can request a full refund within 30 days of your purchase date.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <p>To request a refund:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:dev@aizen.win">dev@aizen.win</a></li>
        <li>Include your order number or the email used for purchase</li>
        <li>Let us know why you are requesting a refund (optional, but helps us improve)</li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        We will process your refund within 5-7 business days. The refund will be credited to your
        original payment method.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>After the 30-Day Period</h2>
      <p>
        Refunds are not available after the 30-day period. However, if you experience technical
        issues that prevent you from using the software, please contact our support team and we will
        do our best to resolve the issue.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Subscription Cancellation</h2>
      <p>
        You can cancel your Pro subscription at any time. Upon cancellation:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>You will retain access until the end of your current billing period</li>
        <li>No further charges will be made</li>
        <li>Pro features will be disabled after the period ends</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Current Pricing</h2>
      <p>
        Aizen Pro is available as a monthly subscription ($5.99/mo), yearly subscription ($59/yr),
        or a one-time Lifetime purchase ($179).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about our refund policy? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:dev@aizen.win">dev@aizen.win</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </LegalPage>
</BaseLayout>
